## For Mod Developers
<hr>

Be sure to add our maven to your `build.gradle`:
```gradle
repositories {
    maven { url = "https://maven.resourcefulbees.com/repository/maven-public/" }
    <--- other repositories here --->
}
```
You can then add our mod as a dependency:

### Forge:
```gradle
dependencies {
    <--- Other dependencies here --->
    implementation fg.deobf("com.teamresourceful.resourcefullib:resourcefullib-forge-${minecraft}:${version}")
}
```

### Fabric:
```gradle
dependencies {
    <--- Other dependencies here --->
    implementation "com.teamresourceful.resourcefullib:resourcefullib-fabric-${minecraft}:${version}"
}
```

### Architectury:

#### Common `build.gradle`
```gradle
dependencies {
    <--- Other dependencies here --->
    modImplementation "com.teamresourceful.resourcefullib:resourcefullib-common-${minecraft}:${version}"
}
```

#### Fabric `build.gradle`
